ion work.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aPushto languagexGrammar. 4aPashto. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aIndo-European Languages.  aPashto.1 aBrugman, Claudia M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrugman, Claudia, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDavid, Anne Boyle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFox, Melissa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoodman, Sarah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMaxwell, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMiller, Corey, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTwist, Alina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Linguistics and Semiotics  2000-2014 (EN)z978311023845708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Backlist 2000-2015z978311074296108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LINGUISTICS 2013z978311031724408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK 2013z9783110317237oZDB-23-DSP0 cprintz978161451303240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161451231840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781614512318423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781614512318/original  a978